Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.75,0:00:11.59,OP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,现在在你眼前 有着无限的未来
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.40,0:00:18.06,OP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,照亮了一切
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.14,0:00:21.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn微软雅黑\fs38\pos(450,390)\1c&HFFFFFF&}海底两万里 / {\fs18}蓝宝石之谜
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.11,0:00:30.21,OP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,讨厌懦弱的人 无法背叛蓝天
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.28,0:00:36.74,OP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,在做梦之前 我想翱翔天际
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.26,0:00:44.29,OP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,心中的音乐盒开启 发出声响
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.36,0:00:51.57,OP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,一点一滴演奏出幸福与勇气
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.64,0:01:00.34,OP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,现在在你眼前 有着无限的未来
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.41,0:01:05.78,OP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,言语是永远的信号
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.85,0:01:10.79,OP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Don't forget to try in mind
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.86,0:01:15.73,OP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,爱比宝石
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.56,0:01:22.36,OP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,更能照亮一切
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.87,0:01:29.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,强他们在无人岛上 建立的科学文明
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.54,0:01:33.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,由于突然登陆的台风 所带来的狂风暴雨巨浪
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.95,0:01:36.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,仅仅一个晚上就全数毁灭
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.92,0:01:41.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,而台风竟然还带来一座新的岛屿
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.62,0:01:44.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,大自然的威力真令人惊讶
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.76,0:01:47.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,即刻动身到岛上探险的强他们
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.29,0:01:48.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,竟然遇到旧识艾尔顿
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.06,0:01:52.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,以及他口中所说的恐怖大王
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.80,0:01:54.89,Title,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,28 漂流岛
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.97,0:01:59.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那就是…恐怖大王
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.14,0:02:01.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那么巨大的动物
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.01,0:02:04.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,应该是史前大怪兽
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.24,0:02:06.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我们会有什么下场？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.31,0:02:12.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,1899年7月 世界将因恐怖大王而毁灭
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.72,0:02:13.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.29,0:02:15.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,大预言
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.02,0:02:18.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,可是那是10年后耶
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.96,0:02:21.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,一定是因为无法一次灭光
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.13,0:02:23.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,所以才打算一点一点的慢慢毁灭
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.40,0:02:24.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,也就是说…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.53,0:02:26.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,先从我们开始
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.57,0:02:28.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,快逃！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.14,0:02:31.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.54,0:02:35.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,等…等等我们
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.98,0:02:47.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好厉害 跑步速度真的变快了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.39,0:02:54.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不光是跑步变快而已喔
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.33,0:02:57.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我跳
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.20,0:03:04.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.47,0:03:08.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这座岛好方便喔
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.17,0:03:11.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我跳
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.17,0:03:35.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,糟…糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.67,0:03:40.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,停下来
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.77,0:03:42.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,停不下来
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.44,0:03:45.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,接下来就交给我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.41,0:03:48.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,哎呀 那些是你的仆人吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.58,0:03:50.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,闭嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.48,0:03:52.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,要杀就杀我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.12,0:03:54.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,他们逃得太快
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.49,0:03:56.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,结果还不是会 绕一圈之后回到原点
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.62,0:03:59.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你这个白痴伯爵 还是没长进
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.39,0:04:02.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我的私人舰队 很快就会找到这座岛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.53,0:04:05.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,到时候就算你们 跪地求饶也没用
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.06,0:04:07.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你的吹牛我已经听腻了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.00,0:04:09.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,认命吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.43,0:04:10.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,OK 那好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.87,0:04:12.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我们来谈条件
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.30,0:04:14.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,保证你们绝不吃亏
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.51,0:04:15.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,给我闭嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.11,0:04:22.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,保证值得一听
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.35,0:04:23.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你就听听看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.55,0:04:25.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,停下来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.89,0:04:32.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,谁快来帮我们停下
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.36,0:04:42.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好痛…停下来了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.40,0:04:44.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.07,0:04:48.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,完全不在乎会为他人带来困扰
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.44,0:04:52.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,葛兰迪丝军团驾到
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.84,0:04:54.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,葛兰迪丝
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.65,0:04:59.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你…你不是娜蒂亚吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.18,0:05:00.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,强
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.62,0:05:01.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,玛莉还有大王
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.15,0:05:04.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,原来你们还活着啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.73,0:05:12.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.20,0:05:14.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,鹦鹉螺号被打败了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.03,0:05:19.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,所以尼莫船长 就让我们先离开船舰
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.34,0:05:23.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那艘万能潜水艇居然会被击沉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.18,0:05:26.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,看来石像鬼的空中战舰 果真是所向披靡
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.91,0:05:29.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那我的尼莫先生也…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.55,0:05:31.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,艾丽朵拉也…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.18,0:05:33.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,大家都死了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.99,0:05:42.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,尼莫先生…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.53,0:05:50.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好大的船
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.14,0:05:51.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,嗯 有够大
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.10,0:05:56.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,没想到这种巨大潜水艇 已经建造成功
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.44,0:05:57.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我真不敢相信
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.51,0:06:01.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这群人懂不懂礼貌啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.85,0:06:04.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,欢迎各位来到本船
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.68,0:06:08.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,用不着对那种不敢露出 真面目的女人报上自己名字
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.85,0:06:11.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,说的也是 是我失礼了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.19,0:06:13.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我名叫艾丽朵拉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.23,0:06:14.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,现在方便吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.49,0:06:16.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你又是什么人？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.93,0:06:18.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,抱歉现在才来和各位见面
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.33,0:06:20.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我是这艘船的船长 尼莫
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.73,0:06:23.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那个…请再说一次您的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.50,0:06:25.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,尼莫 失陪
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.00,0:06:28.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,尼莫…尼莫船长
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.24,0:06:34.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我们无缘再见了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.28,0:06:35.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,没问题的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.05,0:06:38.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,他们一定都还活着
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.18,0:06:40.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,大家不会那么轻易就丧命的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.49,0:06:44.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,才一阵子不见 强也成熟了不少
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.56,0:06:45.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,对吧 娜蒂亚
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.72,0:06:47.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,有吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.26,0:06:49.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你没有看男人的眼光
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.86,0:06:51.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,幸好大家都平安无事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.00,0:06:54.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,因为有我的葛兰坦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.20,0:06:56.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不过 你们在这座岛上 做了些什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.77,0:06:58.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你这句话问得好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.50,0:07:02.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这可是个会让说者与听者 都泪流满面的辛酸史
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.37,0:07:06.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,在鹦鹉螺号 遭石像鬼的空中战舰攻击
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.34,0:07:07.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,面临生死存亡之际
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.95,0:07:09.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我们挺身予以回击
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.45,0:07:13.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.59,0:07:15.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,然后你们就直接逃走了对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.59,0:07:16.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,才不是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.76,0:07:18.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,当时我们即使受到攻击
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.86,0:07:20.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,也尽力将危机化作转机
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.79,0:07:23.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我桑森大爷将一辈子 就那么一回的精湛射击
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.06,0:07:26.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,成功地将子弹打进空中战舰
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.67,0:07:31.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,到这里为止都很顺利
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.74,0:07:34.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,但在那之后 我的葛兰坦的气球破了洞
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.71,0:07:37.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我们也跟着飞到天空的另一头
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.64,0:07:38.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,之后
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.54,0:07:42.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,经过几天的漂流 我们才来到这座岛上
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.41,0:07:47.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,然后才发现这位白痴伯爵 已经先来到这座岛了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.62,0:07:50.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你说我白痴是什么意思？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.69,0:07:54.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我无法忍受你侮蔑 我堂堂艾尔顿伯爵的发言
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.29,0:07:55.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,闭嘴 你这个白痴
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.99,0:07:58.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,骂白痴是白痴有什么不对？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.76,0:07:59.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你这个白痴
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.63,0:08:00.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,居…居然骂了5次
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.97,0:08:03.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你竟然连续骂了我5次白痴
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.70,0:08:06.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你希望的话 我可以再多骂你几次
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.07,0:08:14.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,白痴…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.41,0:08:17.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,所以他说的魔女 指的就是葛兰迪丝啰
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.45,0:08:19.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,魔…魔女？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.08,0:08:21.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,就是这个叔叔说的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.82,0:08:24.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那家伙是个大骗子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.06,0:08:26.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你们也要小心喔
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.93,0:08:28.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,大骗子？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.76,0:08:31.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,还自称是什么伯爵的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.83,0:08:36.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,一个人把我们小心保存下来的酒 全部喝光
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.40,0:08:38.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,所以他才会被埋在沙子里啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.80,0:08:40.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我就觉得不对劲
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.84,0:08:42.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,竟然还把他那些胡说八道当真
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.64,0:08:43.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,也就是说
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.41,0:08:46.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,葛兰坦会跑到这里来 是因为气球破了洞
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.01,0:08:50.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,也因为这样 我们根本无法离开这座岛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.08,0:08:52.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,把气球修好就行啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.85,0:08:56.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,也对 现在有这么多人手 应该会有办法才是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.42,0:08:59.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,感觉好像很久没有闻到 科学的香气了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.96,0:09:02.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,怎么啦 居然说这种感伤话
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.99,0:09:05.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,因为我们一直都待在 什么都没有的岛上啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.33,0:09:07.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这座岛上也是什么都没有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.90,0:09:11.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不过 科学就是从无到有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.17,0:09:12.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,也对
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.44,0:09:16.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不过 这座岛 似乎不是一般的无人岛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.31,0:09:21.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,虽然从未在岛上发现人迹
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.08,0:09:23.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,但总觉得岛上还有其他人在
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.05,0:09:26.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,所以这座岛还是有问题啰？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.89,0:09:29.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,艾尔顿先生的话 并不全是谎言啰？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.69,0:09:31.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.29,0:09:34.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我既不是骗子 也不是吹牛大王
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.53,0:09:36.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,更不是什么白痴
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.03,0:09:39.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那你到底是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.86,0:09:43.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我乃真正的艾尔顿伯爵
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.64,0:09:46.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,下等人们 再会了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.40,0:09:48.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,怎么了？怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.17,0:09:50.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,再会了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.61,0:09:53.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,他跑掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.38,0:09:56.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,他说『再会』是想跑去哪里？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.11,0:09:58.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,他打算搭我的船开溜
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.88,0:10:00.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你说什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.12,0:10:01.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,岛？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.52,0:10:03.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,就是我们之前住的那座岛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.99,0:10:05.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,就算是要逃好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.19,0:10:07.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这附近有岛可以让他逃走吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.17,0:10:18.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,怎…怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.54,0:10:20.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,岛变小了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.61,0:10:22.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,岛变小了？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.41,0:10:26.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.98,0:10:28.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,真的有座岛耶
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.05,0:10:30.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你们就是从那座岛上过来的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.98,0:10:31.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,对啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.38,0:10:33.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,真是怪了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.85,0:10:36.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,昨天之前明明都没见过 那样的岛屿
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.19,0:10:38.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我们也是啊 韩森
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.12,0:10:41.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这座岛是在昨天夜里 突然出现的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.36,0:10:42.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,怎么可能
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.73,0:10:45.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,昨天以前从未见过的这座岛屿
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.16,0:10:46.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,竟然会突然出现
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.36,0:10:48.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,而且到了夜里 还会变小就表示…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.83,0:10:49.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,请回答
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.83,0:10:51.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,岛正在移动
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.80,0:10:53.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,讨厌 真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.81,0:10:55.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,怎么连强都开始吹起牛皮了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.84,0:10:58.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,可是除此之外就别无可能了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.21,0:11:01.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不过 现实之中 不可能发生这种事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.65,0:11:02.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,韩森
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.41,0:11:03.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,什么事？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.31,0:11:05.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,对科学家来说 什么是最重要的？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.92,0:11:07.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,怎…怎么问起这个了？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.35,0:11:08.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,就是直觉啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.35,0:11:09.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,直觉？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.02,0:11:14.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这个地球还有许多 我们人类未知的事物
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.89,0:11:18.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,而解开那一切 就是我们科学家的义务
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.83,0:11:19.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.03,0:11:23.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,到了明天 太阳又会东升
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.57,0:11:26.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,而我的结论也将获得理论佐证
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.64,0:11:30.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,因此我们得再一次 回到那座岛上不可
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.24,0:11:31.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,为什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.44,0:11:35.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,因为珍贵的百科全书 就在那座岛上
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.02,0:11:44.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,距离已经相隔好远了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.99,0:11:46.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,果然真的有在移动吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.79,0:11:49.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,到了明天或许会离得更远吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.89,0:11:52.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,就搬到桑森他们的岛上去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.33,0:11:54.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,搬到一座奇怪的岛上去住
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.57,0:11:55.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,大家愿意吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.60,0:11:57.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,玛莉比较喜欢那座岛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.57,0:11:58.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,因为大家都在那里啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.04,0:12:00.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,也对
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.24,0:12:01.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,比起只有我们
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.91,0:12:03.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,还是跟大家待在一起 也比较能安心
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.84,0:12:04.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,说的也对
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.11,0:12:06.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,小屋也已经垮了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.44,0:12:07.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这样也刚好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.05,0:12:11.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,如果真如强所说 那座岛正在移动的话
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.48,0:12:14.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,说不定哪天会抵达 我的故乡对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.41,0:12:41.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,快点把盘子洗好 过来帮我的忙
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.51,0:12:43.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,催我也没用啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.28,0:12:45.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,积了这么多没洗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.22,0:12:46.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,根本就洗不完嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.25,0:12:49.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我还得额外为你准备食物
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.09,0:12:51.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,别嘀嘀咕咕的快动手干活
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.99,0:12:53.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那你就别做啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.86,0:12:55.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我又没拜托你 是你自己要擅自准备的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.99,0:12:57.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我还觉得困扰呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.96,0:13:00.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,还是一样那么倔强
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.67,0:13:02.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,如果不快点改改脾气
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.40,0:13:04.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不然小心被强嫌弃喔
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.07,0:13:09.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我开动了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.21,0:13:12.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是大餐耶
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.98,0:13:15.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,哎呀 光这些东西就那么开心
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.81,0:13:18.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你们之前都是吃什么度日？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.22,0:13:21.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我们每天都是吃这些 早就腻了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.49,0:13:25.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,为什么老是这么辣呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.86,0:13:29.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你不满意就别吃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.23,0:13:30.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,对吧 娜蒂亚
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.73,0:13:34.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,她怎么又戴上口罩了？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.07,0:13:37.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,似乎是无法接受鱼的味道
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.84,0:13:39.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,真可怜
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.30,0:13:41.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,竟然无法理解这股香气
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.17,0:13:44.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我吃饱了\N辣死我了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.88,0:13:47.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好 今天来盖小木屋吧\N小木屋？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.45,0:13:49.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,现在的小木屋很挤对吧？\N嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.41,0:13:51.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,所以要盖一间新的小木屋
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.88,0:13:53.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,韩森 强借我用一下
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.92,0:13:55.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,伤脑筋耶
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.12,0:13:58.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我原本打算今天要将葛兰坦的 驱动系统拆解下来修理的说
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.66,0:13:59.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,韩森
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.79,0:14:01.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,今天是洗碗日
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.59,0:14:04.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,要修理的话 先等你把碗盘都洗好了再说
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.13,0:14:07.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,葛兰迪丝
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.57,0:14:08.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,什么事？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.80,0:14:11.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,午餐让我来煮
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.30,0:14:12.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我想要试试看
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.67,0:14:14.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,想煮是无所谓 不过你会吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.27,0:14:16.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我不晓得
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.44,0:14:19.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你就试试看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.51,0:14:22.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,凡事都有头一遭嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.35,0:14:25.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这样我早上就有时间玩了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.35,0:14:29.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,强
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.29,0:14:30.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,什么事？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.59,0:14:32.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你跟娜蒂亚…还顺利吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.06,0:14:35.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,嗯 还算可以吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.19,0:14:37.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那么…已经做了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.03,0:14:40.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,已经做了…什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.47,0:14:42.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,怎么这样问我呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.67,0:14:43.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.87,0:14:45.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,讨厌啦 桑森
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.30,0:14:47.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,会…会吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.17,0:14:51.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我认为如果两情相悦 发生那种事是极为自然的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.31,0:14:53.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不过 我们总是在吵架
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.58,0:14:55.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,一直无法顺利进行
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.21,0:14:57.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好 我就来告诉你一个诀窍吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.98,0:15:01.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,女性都很难抗拒男性的肉体
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.09,0:15:06.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,世上的女性都会为这身 经过锻炼的强健肌肉所倾倒
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.66,0:15:09.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,娜蒂亚应该也期望着 那样的男人出现
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.66,0:15:10.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.03,0:15:13.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,只要运动锻炼身体就行了是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.30,0:15:16.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,用这个来锻炼身体
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.53,0:15:21.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我以前也被女生们 当成软脚虾看不起
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.44,0:15:25.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,于是我便发疯般地锻炼身体
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.14,0:15:27.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,当我变身成健壮的男人之后
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.51,0:15:30.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,就再也没有任何人敢瞧不起我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.82,0:15:31.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,所以 强
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.02,0:15:35.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你一直发明也无法赢得 女孩子的芳心
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.65,0:15:38.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是这一带吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.72,0:15:40.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,就是那里 就是那里
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.22,0:15:41.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.73,0:15:44.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,饭还没煮好吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.46,0:15:45.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,还没好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.76,0:15:48.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,今天是娜蒂亚的特制午餐喔
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.77,0:15:51.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,娜蒂亚在煮饭吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.90,0:15:56.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,味道要觉得有点过辣的程度 才会好吃喔
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.34,0:15:59.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我这样要怎么试味道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.99,0:16:09.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你在做什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.29,0:16:13.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,藉由这样来锻炼身体
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.16,0:16:18.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你打算靠这样 来吸引娜蒂亚对吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.33,0:16:19.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,太明显了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.20,0:16:22.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,会…会吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.50,0:16:24.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不过 没问题的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.30,0:16:29.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,娜蒂亚正为了你 在努力准备午餐呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.31,0:16:32.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,娜蒂亚她吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.85,0:16:37.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这…这是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.82,0:16:39.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,料理啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.85,0:16:42.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,比大姐头的料理还要惊人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.15,0:16:45.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这是娜蒂亚第一次下厨
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.92,0:16:47.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我们就来吃吃看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.13,0:16:50.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.16,0:16:52.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不过 盘子好脏喔
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.60,0:16:54.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是因为你又偷懒开溜
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.33,0:16:55.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,所以娜蒂亚只好自己洗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.93,0:16:59.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,话虽然这么说 但我得去修理葛兰坦…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.84,0:17:01.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,娜蒂亚 很好吃喔
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.61,0:17:02.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,真的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.51,0:17:05.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,虽然外观看起来有点吓…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.48,0:17:08.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你是怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.48,0:17:14.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,强
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.66,0:17:19.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,看来伤得不轻
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.79,0:17:21.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,对不起 强
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.53,0:17:23.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你用不着那么介意
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.36,0:17:28.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,男人是不会轻易放弃 自己喜欢的女人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.54,0:17:32.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,他会原谅我吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.77,0:17:35.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,没问题 没问题的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.51,0:17:38.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,没问题 绝对不会有问题的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.61,0:17:40.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你要我不要原谅娜蒂亚
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.88,0:17:43.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,可是我也不晓得该怎么做好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.51,0:17:46.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这种时候最好就是什么都不做
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.35,0:17:47.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,什么都不做？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.79,0:17:48.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,对
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.65,0:17:51.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,除非对方主动道歉 否则就不开口和她交谈
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.52,0:17:53.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我怎么有办法对她视若无睹
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.96,0:17:54.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,听好了 强
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.96,0:17:56.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,身为科学家
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.26,0:17:59.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,对于无论多细微的错误 都不能原谅
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.66,0:18:02.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,女孩子只要一宠就会得意起来
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.27,0:18:03.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,会吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.83,0:18:05.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,看看我这个例子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.40,0:18:08.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,对大姐头一宠再宠的结果 就是这个下场
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.51,0:18:09.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,会吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.91,0:18:11.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,总之
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.31,0:18:14.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,女人是无法抗拒有学问的男人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.38,0:18:17.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,只要有丰富的知识 女人一定都会为你倾倒
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.62,0:18:20.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我想娜蒂亚 一定也期望着那样的男人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.72,0:18:21.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.99,0:18:24.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我只要继续学习和发明 就够了是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.92,0:18:28.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,可是桑森却说 只要运动就够了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.86,0:18:30.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,要是你照他说的话去做
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.73,0:18:32.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,只会让脑袋里长满肌肉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.23,0:18:34.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,根本就无法得到女生的芳心
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.87,0:18:36.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好 果然还是要靠学习
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.87,0:18:40.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我要靠学习 研究和发明 来得到娜蒂亚的芳心
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.04,0:18:42.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我懂了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.21,0:18:44.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,太阳的移动速度变慢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.61,0:18:47.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,就表示这座岛正向东移动
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.41,0:18:49.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,强 你又在搞发明了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.45,0:18:50.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不是的 桑森
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.05,0:18:53.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我正在计算这座岛的位置
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.18,0:18:54.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是研究吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.25,0:18:56.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那不也跟发明没两样吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.75,0:18:57.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,别做那种事了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.72,0:18:58.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你还是快点健身锻炼吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.92,0:19:02.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不然小心变得跟韩森一样 痴肥臃肿
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.39,0:19:07.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,可是韩森说老是运动的话 会让脑袋也长满肌肉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.10,0:19:08.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.20,0:19:12.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,他错了！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.20,0:19:14.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,而且错得离谱！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.34,0:19:16.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,听好了 强
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.54,0:19:19.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,女人会在男人身上 追求自己缺乏的部分
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.08,0:19:22.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,男人则是会对女人 追求自己没有的部分
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.38,0:19:24.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,女人没有 但男人却有的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.15,0:19:25.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你知道那是什么吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.75,0:19:26.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,胡子吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.98,0:19:28.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不对 是力量
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.69,0:19:29.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,力量？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.65,0:19:32.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,用肌肉与力量来保护 自己喜欢的女人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.72,0:19:33.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,而女人则是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.99,0:19:35.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,则是？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.29,0:19:36.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,煮饭
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.56,0:19:40.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,每天都吃这种饭
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.63,0:19:43.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,就算有再多条命也不够啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.33,0:19:47.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这都要怪大姐头偷懒 饭都让娜蒂亚煮
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.30,0:19:49.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,才不是我偷懒呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.74,0:19:53.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是因为娜蒂亚说她想煮 我才让她试试的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.01,0:19:55.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那你为什么不阻止她呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.88,0:19:57.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这已经是第二次了耶
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.48,0:20:00.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不过才失败个一两次 有什么关系
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.38,0:20:02.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,娜蒂亚一定会愈煮愈好吃的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.42,0:20:03.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不过 在那之前
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.65,0:20:08.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,前途无量的有为青年 恐怕会先蒙主宠召喔 大姐头
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.63,0:20:12.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不过 大姐头煮的饭 也没比娜蒂亚好到哪里去
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.30,0:20:13.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你说什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.40,0:20:17.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你说我什么时候煮过 难吃到会让人丧命的饭了？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.17,0:20:20.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,毕竟娜蒂亚也不是故意的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.54,0:20:22.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你就大人有大量…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.14,0:20:25.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不是故意的 就可以为所欲为了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.81,0:20:28.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你的反应也用不着那么激烈吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.81,0:20:29.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,就是说啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.65,0:20:32.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,饭就是要稍微辣一点才好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.02,0:20:38.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,真想早点离开这座岛 吃点更正常的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.26,0:20:41.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,韩森 你为什么不快把葛兰坦修好？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.16,0:20:44.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,谁教你老是把强抢去用
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.00,0:20:48.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,大家不要再吵了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.13,0:20:50.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,居然为了这种小事吵成一团
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.84,0:20:52.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,大家都好奇怪喔
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.44,0:20:53.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,强
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.94,0:20:56.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,没错 大家在一起的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.11,0:21:00.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,要以让他人感到喜悦为优先 而不是先考虑到自己
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.11,0:21:04.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,如此一来 欢乐也将自然孕育而生
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.05,0:21:08.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这些话似乎挺有道理的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.29,0:21:10.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,听起来就像真正的伯爵一样
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.86,0:21:14.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好怀念啊 自己还在英国的时候…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.46,0:21:21.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我的口袋总是不断发出 满满的金币碰撞声
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.87,0:21:25.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,每到生日就会请来数十位女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.17,0:21:28.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,连开三天三夜的宴会
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.47,0:21:30.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,有从世界各地收藏来的酒
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.17,0:21:33.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,还有你们从未见过的珍奇料理
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.38,0:21:37.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,满满地排在桌上 根本连吃都吃不完
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.55,0:21:41.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.63,0:21:52.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,他人很不错喔
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.36,0:21:53.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你在说谁？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.43,0:21:56.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,愿意替心仪对象 掩饰失败的体贴男人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.67,0:21:58.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,天底下可没那么多喔
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.40,0:21:59.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.04,0:22:03.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你在担心 自己会不会被他嫌弃对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.28,0:22:10.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,没办法啊 那些心情就像是女人的业障
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.08,0:22:10.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,业障？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.85,0:22:13.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,而且是已经有心仪对象的女人
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.29,0:22:17.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,像是嫉妒 执着 不安
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.32,0:22:19.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那些无法用言语来表达的感情
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.62,0:22:22.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,就如同洪水般占据了脑海
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.76,0:22:25.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,让人根本无暇顾及其它
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.03,0:22:30.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这就叫恋爱
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.40,0:22:36.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我一直以来 都没办法喜欢上别人
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.07,0:22:38.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不 是我不愿意去喜欢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.88,0:22:43.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不过 这跟我一直在脑海中 想像的情况不同
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.11,0:22:44.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你是指强吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.72,0:22:46.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.15,0:22:50.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我没想到喜欢上别人 竟然是件如此难受的事
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.99,0:22:51.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.02,0:22:56.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我也曾为了那样的情感 而无数次泪湿枕头
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.73,0:22:58.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.26,0:23:00.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那种时候我就会想到
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.63,0:23:03.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我终究还是个女人
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.34,0:23:06.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,娜蒂亚
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.40,0:23:07.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,什么事？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.37,0:23:11.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你的父亲真的是尼莫船长吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.81,0:23:16.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,抱歉 问了你这种怪问题
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.51,0:23:19.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,没关系 反正是事实啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.32,0:23:22.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这让我觉得好感伤喔
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.59,0:23:26.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,可是你还有桑森与韩森啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.76,0:23:30.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,他们就像月亮一样
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.93,0:23:34.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,总是在我身边绕啊绕的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.23,0:23:36.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,却不会更靠近过来
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.90,0:23:41.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,对了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.07,0:23:41.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,怎么了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.01,0:23:45.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,以后你就叫我妈妈吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.41,0:23:46.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,妈妈？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.54,0:23:50.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,因为尼莫船长是你的爸爸啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.08,0:23:52.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,妈妈…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.38,0:23:54.85,Title,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,待续
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.92,0:24:02.85,ED,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,该怎么应付心中的焦急才好？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.93,0:24:08.06,ED,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,就要看不清远方的梦想了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.13,0:24:12.43,ED,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我喃喃自语 仰望星空
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.50,0:24:21.34,ED,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,与你的约定耀眼闪烁着
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.41,0:24:31.41,ED,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Try 安慰的话语 是传达不到内心的风
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.49,0:24:40.23,ED,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,虽然背负的不安逐渐膨胀
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.30,0:24:44.50,ED,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,但这是我自己的决定
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.57,0:24:49.16,ED,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我一个人应该也不要紧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:49.24,0:24:58.41,ED,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,即使跌倒或感到迷惘 仍然有明天
Dialogue: 0,0:25:07.93,0:25:10.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,桑森与韩森吵架了
Dialogue: 0,0:25:10.79,0:25:15.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,然后艾尔顿很难得地 提出一个有建设性的解决办法
Dialogue: 0,0:25:15.37,0:25:17.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,桑森用真正的大王
Dialogue: 0,0:25:17.74,0:25:20.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,韩森则制作出机械的大王
Dialogue: 0,0:25:20.44,0:25:24.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,彼此竞争 输的人就要乖乖听赢的人的话
Dialogue: 0,0:25:24.24,0:25:26.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不过啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:25:26.21,0:25:30.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,海底两万里 下一回 『大王对大王』
Dialogue: 0,0:25:30.48,0:25:31.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,要看喔
